			"height":150
		},
		{"file":"🍀 花园导览/🧰 本库指南/📂 本库目录及插件介绍.md","id":"basics4","type":"file","x":-800,"y":650,"width":300,"height":150},
		{
			"id":"basics5",
			"styleAttributes":{"shape":"document"},
			"text":"## 📚 推荐学习资源\n\n### 官方资源\n- [Obsidian 官方文档](https://help.obsidian.md/)\n- [Obsidian 社区论坛](https://forum.obsidian.md/)\n\n### 视频教程\n- Johnny学 3小时入门课\n- 简睿学堂插件系列\n\n### 文章教程\n- 少数派 Obsidian 专栏\n- PKMer 知识管理社区",
			"type":"text",
			"x":-1150,
			"y":850,
			"width":600,
			"height":280,
			"color":"2"
		},
		{
			"id":"core1",
			"styleAttributes":{"shape":"diamond"},
			"text":"## 🔍 搜索与查询\n- 全局搜索技巧\n- 搜索运算符\n- 正则表达式\n- 标签与链接过滤",
			"type":"text",
			"x":-350,
			"y":450,
			"width":300,
			"height":150
		},
		{"id":"tips1","text":"## 💡 学习建议\n\n1. **循序渐进**：不要贪多\n2. **实践为主**：边学边用\n3. **定期回顾**：温故知新\n4. **社区交流**：共同成长","type":"text","x":-1200,"y":1400,"width":400,"height":200,"color":"1"},
		{
			"id":"resourceslink",
