		},
		{"id":"core3","text":"## 📝 模板系统\n- 核心模板功能\n- 模板变量\n- 日期格式化\n- 自动化创建","type":"text","x":-350,"y":650,"width":300,"height":150},
		{
			"id":"welcome",
			"styleAttributes":{"border":"solid","shape":"pill","textAlign":"center"},
			"text":"# 🚀 Obsidian 从入门到精通\n\n## 完整学习路线图\n\n> 从零基础到专家级用户的进阶之路\n\n**预计学习时间：3-6个月**",
			"type":"text",
			"x":0,
			"y":0,
			"width":500,
			"height":200,
			"color":"4"
		},
		{"file":"🍀 花园导览/🧰 本库指南/Tutorials/» Daily notes工作流.md","id":"core2","type":"file","x":0,"y":450,"width":300,"height":150},
		{"file":"Extras/Templates/∑ 模板文件创建入口.md","id":"core4","type":"file","x":0,"y":650,"width":300,"height":150},
		{
			"id":"plugin1",
			"styleAttributes":{"shape":"predefined-process"},
			"text":"## 🔌 必装插件清单\n\n### 核心增强\n- **Dataview**: 动态查询与数据视图\n- **Templater**: 高级模板引擎\n- **QuickAdd**: 快速创建与自动化\n\n### 编辑增强\n- **Advanced Tables**: 表格编辑\n- **Calendar**: 日历视图\n- **Excalidraw**: 手绘图表",
			"type":"text",
			"x":450,
			"y":450,
			"width":600,
			"height":320
		},
		{
			"id":"core5",
			"styleAttributes":{"shape":"parallelogram"},
			"text":"## 🎨 Canvas 画布\n\n### 基础操作\n- 创建和连接节点\n- 分组与颜色管理\n- 嵌入文件和链接\n\n### 高级技巧\n- Portal 功能\n- 跨维度连接\n- 自定义样式",
			"type":"text",
			"x":-350,
			"y":850,
			"width":600,
			"height":280,
			"color":"1"
		},
		{
			"id":"advanced1",
			"styleAttributes":{"shape":"database"},
			"text":"## 🗃️ 知识管理体系\n\n- **Zettelkasten** 卡片盒笔记法\n- **PARA** 方法论实践\n- **ACCESS** 工作流\n- **MOC** 内容地图构建",
			"type":"text",
			"x":1250,
			"y":450,
			"width":600,
			"height":200
		},
		{"file":"🍀 花园导览/🧰 本库指南/Tutorials/∑ 本库 ACCESS 工作流汇总.md","id":"advanced2","type":"file","x":1250,"y":700,"width":300,"height":150},
		{
			"id":"workflowcenter",
			"styleAttributes":{"shape":"circle","textAlign":"center"},
			"text":"# 🔄 工作流整合\n\n将所有知识点整合成个人工作流：\n\n**输入** → **处理** → **连接** → **输出**\n\nInbox → Cards → Atlas → Published",
